### HYMN XXII

#### To Savitar, or Yama invested with Savitar's attributes

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0702201">1</span></span>Unto a
thousand sages he hath given sight: thought, light is he  
   in ranging all.  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0702202">2</span></span>The Bright
One hath sent forth the Dawns, a closely gathered  
   band,  
  Immaculate, unanimous, brightly refulgent in their homes.

